{"tid":1099942,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"一件小事已經可以睇到香港有班咁偽善嘅人","createTime":"2019-04-10T06:10:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-10T07:15:20.000Z","uid":211721,"like":19,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"b9bcfb6bd2026e9466bba137d7609254a33dd5b3","tid":1099942,"uid":211721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-10T06:10:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KiJQgfi.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKiJQgfi.png&h=1f46a1ae&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n一件好事開幕， 對香港動物醫學有好嘅幫助<br />\n只不過係劏隻燒豬慶祝下件盛事， 就有一堆撚樣係到話身為動物醫院， 唔應該切隻燒豬嚟慶祝 <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">你班撚樣係咪唔食豬肉食開屎㗎 ，見到一車一車豬運入屠場留馬尿，開始戒食豬肉？ 弱撚智</span></span></span><br />\n仲有啊，好多留言話多諷刺 ，我見你班偽善臭化閪就真係多諷刺<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">愛護動物還愛護動物，依家連食肉嘅權利都要剝削？</span></span><br />\n<br />\n有興趣睇班偽善撚嘅留言可以去cityu fb page<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71f50e125ff7727208aee08aa02988f38b5f5541","tid":1099942,"uid":211721,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-10T06:13:03.000Z","msg":"好撚on9 <br />\n咁撚弱智嘅人都有<br />\n唔知啲人係見風使舵，見到多數人屌就屌埋一份<br />\n定真係好撚偽善<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">好撚嘔心呀你班食屎狗</span>"},{"pid":"c7d67c6851a016984c90c39c1c1983097954005e","tid":1099942,"uid":3501,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-10T06:14:58.000Z","msg":"素食撚係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 食隻豬就喊打喊殺"},{"pid":"85762ecaad13885100757ed362b73e49f9e113bd","tid":1099942,"uid":52155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-10T06:15:08.000Z","msg":"其實城大咁做真係出嚟搞笑 但係下面班仲搞笑 成班道德判官咁 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5776fc65b6d5471641f0129026b133cae944cedd","tid":1099942,"uid":211721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c7d67c6851a016984c90c39c1c1983097954005e","